Package project4

Class Service

  • java.lang.Object
    • project4.Service

  • public class Service
extends java.lang.Object
    The Service class implements the service provided to a member. It contains 2 constructors that initializes its serviceName, serviceNumber, and serviceFee fields to the appropriate strings and/or doubles it is passed. It also has a comparator to compare any 2 service names, along with setters and getters for the aforementioned fields.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Alan Manning
